<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="species">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Appr. 150 species. The largest genus in 
<taxonomicName family="Asteraceae" genus="Scorzonerinae" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Scorzonerinae" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="genus">Scorzonerinae</taxonomicName>
after splitting of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Compositae" genus="Scorzonera" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Scorzonera" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Scorzonera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
